HEADWORD: Registrant
<hw>Reg"is*trant</hw> <pr>(-tr<it>a</it>nt)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>registrans</ets>, p. pr.]</ety> <def>One who registers; esp., one
who , by virtue of securing an official registration, obtains a certain
right or title of possession, as to a trade-mark.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

